      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIGHWAY TO HELL (1) jumps from the inside draw. Latest effort finished 6th over 350m at this track beaten 3.5 lengths (20.21) behind Darra Mick in a T3 RSTW on April 3. Looks well placed and should feature. DART NIGHTS (4) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Bottom Up - Maiden winner (17.48) three back at this track. Can turn it around this time. TAKE A VIOLET (2) was a little disappointing last start at Warragul when 4th (23.71) over 400m. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including one win. Likely to play a prominent role. WALTZING ARIA (7) can sneak into the finish while fresh.",
